                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1657" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0265</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8837 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">借微博之力看浙江省旅游局如何玩转“微营销”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does the Zhejiang Tourism Bureau boom “micro marketing” via Micro-blog</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄浏英，周亚庆等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江省旅游局</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">旅游官方微博；微营销；互联网思维；新媒介传播</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">tourism official micro-blog；micro marketing；internet thinking；new media communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了作为官方旅游主管部门的浙江省旅游局，在微营销时代下如何积极投身微营销的基本历程以及面临的新问题。作为旅游大省的旅游主管部门，浙江省旅游局较早地意识到微营销的重要性，早在2011率先开通了旅游官方微博并授权浙江省旅游信息中心开始试水微博营销，一度取得了骄人的成绩。此后，微信的出现及流行，不可避免地挤占用户在微博上停留的时间，微信成为微营销领域的又一匹黑马并对微博形成了强劲的挑战。对于浙江省旅游局而言，是继续开展旅游微博营销还是转战微信营销？旅游微博和旅游微信到底是竞争关系还是互补关系？互联网时代如何有效整合资源玩转“微营销”实现营销效果的最大化？这是摆在浙江省旅游局以及微营销主要负责部门——浙江省旅游信息中心面前的新课题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the basic process of how the Tourism Bureau of Zhejiang Province responded to the new trend and took an active part in micro-marketing in the age of micro-marketing, as well as the new problems it confronted. As the tourism administration of a leading tourism province, the Tourism Bureau of Zhejiang Province realized an earlier importance of micro-marketing and launched the first tourism official microblog to dip its toes in microblog marketing in 2011. And this attempt achieved a proud feat. Before long, the emergence and population of WeChat inevitably occupied users’ time that distributed to Microblog. WeChat became a growing power in micro-marketing area   and challenged the position of microblog marketing. Therefore, a tough choice faced the The Tourism Bureau of Zhejiang Province, to continue the  Microblog marketing or to replace it with Wechat marketing? What is the relationship between tourism Microblog and WeChat? Complementary or competitive? How to integrate resources and take full advantage of micro marketing so as to maximize the marketing effect in the internet age? These were the new questions that the Information Center of Zhejiang Province must face. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《旅游市场营销》、《旅游目的地管理》、《营销管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">微营销、新媒介传播、互联网 思维、营销创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-09</td>
                            </tr>
